                    <div class="col-md-10">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <h3><b>Smart Search</b></h3>
                                <p style="padding-top: 10px">Accurately search through tens of thousands of classes in a matter of seconds.</p><br>
                                    <img src="/images/list.png" style="width:40px;height:40px;">                                
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <h3><b>Easy Planning</b></h3>
                                <p style="padding-top: 10px">Don't waste hours of time planning next quarter's class schedule.</p><br>
                                    <br><img src="/images/watch.png" style="width:40px;height:40px;">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <h3><b>In-Depth Reviews</b></h3>
                                <p style="padding-top: 10px">Find out about class information, difficulty, professor's rating and other students' reviews, all in one place.</p>
                                    <br><img src="/images/detail.png" style="width:40px;height:40px;">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-1"></div>                    
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="grey">           
                    <div class="col-md-5  col-xs-12" style="margin-left: 100px; margin-top: 75px;">
                        <img src="/images/imac.png" style="width:467px;height:350px;">                            
                    </div>                    
                    <div class="col-md-5">
                        <h3 style="padding-top: 100px"><b>Tired of CAESAR?</b></h3>
                            <p style="padding-top: 10px">We all know how frustrating CAESAR's slow and unfriendly search process is.
                                Brutus lets you search through every single Northwestern University course in a fraction of the time.
                            </p>
                            <p style="padding-top: 10px"><font size="2">Brutus search has all courses offered since 2010.</p>
                            <p style="padding-top: 10px"><font size="2">Brutus uses NU API to update the course list everyday to provide most up to a date information.</p>                         
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-2"></div>                      
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="container" style="padding-top: 225px">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="white">
                    <div class="col-md-1"></div>                                 
                    <div class="col-md-5">
                        <h3 style="padding-top: 100px"><b>Plan your classes in minutes,<br> not hours</b></h3>
                            <p style="padding-top: 10px"><font size="3">Worrying about degree requirements is stressful enough as it is. 
                                Nobody should be forced to spend hours and hours sifting through CTECS just to determine which professor to take a class with.
                                <br><br>With Brutus, you can find out all the necessary information about a class all
                                on one easy-to-read page.
                            </p>
                    </div>                      
                    <div class="col-md-6" style="margin-top: 75px;">
                        <img src="/images/ipad.png" style="width:467px;height:350px;">                        
                    </div>                                      
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
