                    <div class="col-md-5">
                        <h3 style="padding-top: 100px"><b>Personalized Data</b></h3>
                            <p style="padding-top: 10px">Ever wondered which classes students rate as the most challenging?
                                How about the best professor for a given class? Want to see how your GPA progresses? 
                                <br><br>Find out today on Brutus!
                            </p>                                                     
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-2"></div>                      
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="container" style="padding-top: 1125px">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="white2">
                    <div class="col-md-2"></div>                                 
                    <div class="col-md-4">
